                        footer
                            a.github.holo-button(href='https://github.com/tastejs')
                                | Fork on Github
                            a.website.holo-button(href='http://tastejs.com')
                                | tastejs.com

                div.tile-screen-brick.web(style='background-image: url(images/projects/passyme.jpg)')
                    header passy.me
                    .inner
                        p.description
                            | This very website. Built with Yeoman, Jade,
